text: Eugene McGovern (born 25 May 1982)Eugene McGovern player profile munsterrugby.ie is an Irish rugby union player, playing in the prop position.Eugene McGovern profile Sky Sports He played for Munster from 2002 until 2007, making his debut for Munster against Newport Gwent Dragons in October 2003. From Limerick, McGovern was educated at Crescent College. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Irish rugby union players Category:Rugby union props Category:Munster Rugby players Category:Garryowen Football Club players Category:Rugby union players from County Limerick Category:People educated at Crescent College
